                  'http://www.nicerodds.co.uk/olympics-biathlon-men-relay',
                  'http://www.nicerodds.co.uk/olympics-biathlon-women-7-5-km-sprint',
                  'http://www.nicerodds.co.uk/olympics-biathlon-women-10-km-pursuit',
