                  'http://www.nicerodds.co.uk/olympics-biathlon-mixed-relay')
                )

biathlon <- lapply(urls, nicerodds_scraper)
biathlon <- do.call(bind_rows, biathlon)
biathlon$sport <- "biathlon"

all_events <- alpine %>%
  bind_rows(biathlon)
